OL,3,CHusband: 'I didn't help my wife
OL,4,Cbecause she intended to end her life'
OL,6,FA husband has told a jury he didn't
OL,7,Finitially seek medical help for his
OL,8,Fwife because she had "intended to end
OL,9,Fher life" and he didn't want to go
OL,10,Fagainst her wishes.
OL,12,FDorothy Morgan, who was 71, died in
OL,13,Fhospital on 4 February 2021.
OL,15,FWhen admitted several days earlier, on
OL,16,F25 January, 5ft 1in Mrs Morgan was
OL,17,Ffound to be clinically dehydrated and
OL,18,Fseverely malnourished. She weighed
OL,19,Fonly four and a half stones.
