OL,6,FA pathologist concluded that the cause
OL,7,Fof her death was severe emaciation and
OL,8,F` as a result of being immobile for a
OL,9,Fsignificant period of time ` neglected
OL,10,Finfected pressure ulcers.
OL,12,FMrs Morgan's husband, Robert Morgan,
OL,13,F61, and her son by another man, 53-
OL,14,Fyear-old David Holyoak, are both on
OL,15,Ftrial at Carlisle Crown Court.
OL,17,FThey deny a charge of manslaughter
OL,18,Fwhich alleges that they unlawfully
OL,19,Fkilled their respective wife and
OL,20,Fmother by gross negligence.
