OL,6,FToday, Morgan ` who met his wife in
OL,7,F1997 ` gave evidence. He told jurors
OL,8,FMrs Morgan retired at the age of 65
OL,9,Fbut then, around two years later,
OL,10,Fbegan to lose interest in gardening,
OL,11,Fcharity work and cleaning the Calder
OL,12,FAvenue home at Whitehaven in which all
OL,13,Fthree family members lived.
