OL,3,CHusband: 'I didn't help my wife
OL,4,Cbecause she intended to end her life'
OL,6,F"Were you able to find out what she
OL,7,Fintended?" Mr English asked.
OL,9,F"Yes," Morgan replied. "She intended
OL,10,Fto end her life."
OL,12,FTwo or three times a week, said
OL,13,FMorgan, he would suggest or tell her
OL,14,Fto see a doctor. "She said she was
OL,15,Ffine. That there was nothing wrong.
OL,16,FShe wasn't going to change," he told
OL,17,Fjurors.
OL,19,FShe cut down on food and drink but
OL,20,Fcontinued to smoke heavily.
