OL,3,CHusband: 'I didn't help my wife
OL,4,Cbecause she intended to end her life'
OL,6,F"What would have happened if you had
OL,7,Fgot some help for her?" asked Mr
OL,8,FEnglish.
OL,10,F"I don't think she would have accepted
OL,11,Fit," said Morgan.
OL,13,F"Did you think it was something you
OL,14,Fshould do, or try to do?" asked the
OL,15,Fbarrister.
OL,17,F"I tried. We (Holyoak also) tried to
OL,18,Fpersuade her," replied Morgan. "She
OL,19,Fhad just set herself down that road
OL,20,Fand she was going to get to the end of
OL,21,Fit."
