OL,6,FNor did he detect what a geriatrician
OL,7,Fwould later describe as a "very strong
OL,8,Fsmell" from the pressure sores she
OL,9,Fhad. "At no time was there a strong
OL,10,Fsmell. The only smell off her was the
OL,11,Fstench of cigarettes," said Morgan.
OL,13,F"Did you know that she had sores or
OL,14,Finjuries like that?" Mr English asked
OL,15,Fhim.
