OL,3,CHusband: 'I didn't help my wife
OL,4,Cbecause she intended to end her life'
OL,6,F"Not at any time," said Morgan. "I
OL,7,Fnever knew she had any sores. If I had
OL,8,Fseen any sores or she had mentioned
OL,9,Fany sores or even said she was in
OL,10,Fpain, I would have sent her to the
OL,11,Fhospital. I wouldn't have waited."
OL,13,FHe said Mrs Morgan only ever mentioned
OL,14,Fpain in her knees.
OL,16,FBut the "game changed", he said, on 25
OL,17,FJanuary ` his birthday ` after her
OL,18,Fcondition had significantly worsened.
