OL,3,CHusband: 'I didn't help my wife
OL,4,Cbecause she intended to end her life'
OL,6,FHe sought an on-call doctor's help at
OL,7,Ffirst but then recalled dialling 999
OL,8,Fafter Holyoak told Mrs Morgan was
OL,9,Funresponsive.
OL,11,FMr English asked: "Before that, did
OL,12,Fyou think she needed any medical help?"
OL,14,FMorgan responded: "If I could persuade
OL,15,Fher, then yes, I would have got her
OL,16,Fmedical help. But if she was not
OL,17,Fwilling to accept, no, I wouldn't have
OL,18,Fdone.
